== 歷史 ==
[[File:Court_Square_entrance_vc.jpg|thumb]]資助下進行翻新]]
此站的第一個啟用部分為45路-法庭屋廣場，於1916年11月5日啟用，根據{{link-en|雙重合約|Dual Contracts}}將[[IRT法拉盛線|IRT法拉盛線]]由[[亨特斯角大道車站_(IRT法拉盛線)|亨特斯角大道車站]]延長至[[皇后區廣場車站|皇后區廣場車站]]的兩站延伸的一部分<ref name="er">{{Citation|last=Rogoff|first=David|title=The Steinway Tunnels|date=April 1960|url=http://www.nycsubway.org/articles/steinwaytunnels.html|quote=A station was erected midway at 11th St. and is now known as ‘45th Rd.-Court House Square’. Operation was extended to Hunters Point Ave. on the eastbound track on Feb. 15th, 1916, and to Queensboro Plaza on the following Nov. 5th, opening Court House Square station.|journal=Electric Railroads|issue=29|publisher=Electric Railroaders’ Association|accessdate=2011-05-30|archive-date=2012-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120805130548/http://www.nycsubway.org/articles/steinwaytunnels.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nyt-1916-11-05">{{cite news |title=New Subway Link |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9D05E5D81439E233A25756C0A9679D946796D6CF |newspaper=The New York Times |date=1916-11-05 |page=XX4 |accessdate=2011-10-02 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115040/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9D05E5D81439E233A25756C0A9679D946796D6CF |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1920年代末至1930年代初，城市擁有的[[獨立地鐵系統|獨立地鐵系統]]（IND）興建了首段的[[IND跨城線|跨城線]]與[[IND皇后林蔭路線|皇后林蔭路線]]；法庭廣場的跨區線車站是兩條路線首次在皇后區興建車站，結構於1930年7月完工，並繼續安裝瓷磚和其他設備<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930">{{cite news|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252015%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201930%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201930%2520-%25202102.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2Fbf5dfe364c64162631341118e54b9106#page=1|title=Court Square Station Of New Tube Completed; War Over Van Alst Ave.|last=|first=|date=1930-07-19|work=Long Island Daily Star|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|page=1|via=Fulton History|accessdate=2016-07-27}}</ref><ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930-pg3">{{cite news|url=http://fultonhistory.com/Newspaper%2015/Brooklyn%20NY%20Daily%20Star/Brooklyn%20NY%20Daily%20Star%201930/Brooklyn%20NY%20Daily%20Star%201930%20-%202104.pdf|title=Court Square Station Of New Tube Completed; War Over Van Alst Ave.|last=|first=|date=1930-07-19|work=Long Island Daily Star|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|page=3|access-date=|via=|accessdate=2016-07-27}}</ref>。1933年8月19日，IND跨城線第一段開放了法庭廣場車站。介乎曼哈頓和[[傑克遜高地-羅斯福大道車站_(IND皇后林蔭路線)|羅斯福大道車站]]的一段IND皇后林蔭路線於同日啟用，GG線列車（現時G線列車前身）在[[皇后廣場車站_(IND皇后林蔭路線)|皇后廣場車站]]和布魯克林的[[納蘇大道車站_(IND跨城線)|納蘇大道車站]]營運<ref name="NYTimes-INDQBLCrstwnOpen-1933"/><ref name="LIDaily-QBL-CrosstownOpen-Aug1933">{{cite news|title=New Queens Subway Service Will Be Launched Tonight; Tunnel From Manhattan Open to Jackson Heights; Service Will Eventually Be Extended Through To Jamaica|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252014%2FJamaica%2520NY%2520Long%2520Island%2520Daily%2520Press%2FJamaica%2520NY%2520Long%2520Island%2520Daily%2520Press%25201933%2FJamaica%2520NY%2520Long%2520Island%2520Daily%2520Press%25201933%2520-%25204319.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F4b038616712c5736ea2d11c006e2761c#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=Long Island Daily Press|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=1933-08-18|page=20|archive-date=2021-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211013152456/https://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%2014%2FJamaica%20NY%20Long%20Island%20Daily%20Press%2FJamaica%20NY%20Long%20Island%20Daily%20Press%201933%2FJamaica%20NY%20Long%20Island%20Daily%20Press%201933%20-%204319.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F4b038616712c5736ea2d11c006e2761c#page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。23街-埃利大道車站部分於1930年代早期興建<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930"/><ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930-pg3"/><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen1-1939" /><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939" /><ref name="BklynEagle-23Ely-Jan1939"/>，但直至1939年8月28日E線列車營運時才開放<ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen1-1939" /><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939" />。

=== 新建連接 ===
1984年，MTA計劃在皇后林蔭路線和跨城線之間興建轉乘通道，連接皇后林蔭路線和[[63街線|IND 63街線]]<ref name="QueensSubwayEIS-1984" /><ref name="NYTimes-63rdExtend-Dec1980" />。大約1986年，[[花旗集團|花旗集團]]同意資助轉乘通道以850萬美元作為鄰近{{link-en|法庭廣場1號|One Court Square}}塔的地帶要求而興建<ref name="NYCDCP-NYCTBonus" /><ref name="NYTimes-1CtSq-Giant-Aug1988">{{cite news|last1=DePalma|first1=Anthony|title=A Giant to Dominate Low-Rise Queens|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1988/08/07/realestate/a-giant-to-dominate-low-rise-queens.html?pagewanted=all|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1988-08-07|archive-date=2019-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812104627/https://www.nytimes.com/1988/08/07/realestate/a-giant-to-dominate-low-rise-queens.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Oser|first1=Alan S.|title=Perspectives: Offices in Queens; British Airways Lands in Jackson Heights|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1987/05/17/realestate/perspectives-offices-in-queens-british-airways-lands-in-jackson-heights.html|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1987-05-17|archive-date=2019-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811104945/https://www.nytimes.com/1987/05/17/realestate/perspectives-offices-in-queens-british-airways-lands-in-jackson-heights.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes-1CourtSq-Misfit-Feb1994" />；該塔作為花旗集團將其營運分散至不同大廈的過程一部分<ref name=":0" />。同時該公司選擇該處亦因為鄰近此站<ref name=":0">{{cite news|last1=Gottlieb|first1=Martin|title=CITICORP, TO DECENTRALIZE, PLANS QUEENS COMPLEX|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1985/12/16/nyregion/citicorp-to-decentralize-plans-queens-complex.html|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1985-12-16|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815163831/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/12/16/nyregion/citicorp-to-decentralize-plans-queens-complex.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該大廈於1989年開放，而轉乘通道後來也完工<ref name="NYTimes-1CourtSq-Misfit-Feb1994" />2000年，MTA開始設計第二條付費區內來往法拉盛線和跨城線的轉乘通道<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bertrand|first1=Donald|title=$7M SLATED FOR FENCING, RAIL & SUBWAY STATION PLANS|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/boroughs/7m-slated-fencing-rail-subway-station-plans-article-1.871495|accessdate=2016-07-28|work=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|Daily News (New York)]]|date=2000-05-15|archive-date=2018-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102072845/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/boroughs/7m-slated-fencing-rail-subway-station-plans-article-1.871495|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=CONSTRUCT TRANSFER BETWEEN COURT SQUARE STATION & COURTHOUSE SQUARE STATION QUEENS|url=http://www.mta.nyc.ny.us/mta/eye-nyct.htm#c32998|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2016-12-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000816070400/http://www.mta.nyc.ny.us/mta/eye-nyct.htm#c32998|archivedate=2000-08-16|deadurl=yes|date=2000}}</ref>。2001年12月16日，63街線聯絡線啟用，皇后林蔭路線的服務亦得以加強，G線列車需要在平日以法庭廣場為總站。為了補償前往皇后區的跨城線乘客，法拉盛線亦加入了免費閘外轉乘<ref name="MTA-GLineReview-2013" /><ref name="nyt 200105" />。

2005年10月，花旗集團宣佈會資助法拉盛線和跨城線的轉乘通道，作為法庭廣場2號大樓的又一項地帶要求<ref name="TimesLedger-CtSqTransfer-Jun2011">{{cite news|last1=Henely|first1=Rebecca|title=LIC subway station opens|url=http://www.timesledger.com/stories/2011/24/at_court_square_stop_20110609.html|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=Times Ledger|date=2011-06-15|archive-date=2018-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614194714/https://www.timesledger.com/stories/2011/24/at_court_square_stop_20110609.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=MAYOR BLOOMBERG, QUEENS BOROUGH PRESIDENT MARSHALL AND CITIGROUP BREAK GROUND ON 15-STORY OFFICE TOWER IN LONG ISLAND CITY: Mayor Announces Nearly $50 Million Commitment to Fund Area Infrastructure Improvements|url=http://www.nyc.gov/portal/site/nycgov/menuitem.c0935b9a57bb4ef3daf2f1c701c789a0/index.jsp?pageID=mayor_press_release&catID=1194&doc_name=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fhtml%2Fom%2Fhtml%2F2005b%2Fpr406-05.html&cc=unused1978&rc=1194&ndi=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=[[Government_of_New_York_City|News from the Blue Room]]|date=2005-10-26|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817051742/http://www.nyc.gov/portal/site/nycgov/menuitem.c0935b9a57bb4ef3daf2f1c701c789a0/index.jsp?pageID=mayor_press_release&catID=1194&doc_name=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fhtml%2Fom%2Fhtml%2F2005b%2Fpr406-05.html&cc=unused1978&rc=1194&ndi=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年3月7日，皇后林蔭路線車站改名「法庭廣場-23街車站」（{{lang|en|Court Square–23rd Street}}）<ref name="MTA-23Ely-Mar172001" />。同年6月3日，花費4700萬美元興建符合[[美國殘疾人法案|無障礙通行]]的連接通道啟用，兩站同日改名為「法庭廣場車站」，大部分計劃由花旗資助，另有1390萬美元由MTA負責<ref name="TimesLedger-CtSqTransfer-Jun2011" /><ref name="MTA-CourtSqTransfer-Jun2011" />。法拉盛線車站於2012年1月21日至4月2日亦關閉進行進一步翻新，包括升級月台和翻新車站夾層，以讓車站完全符合無障礙要求<ref name="MTA-IRTCourtSq-Apr22012">{{cite news|title=Court Square on the No.7 Line Re-Opens|url=http://www.mta.info/news/2012/04/02/court-square-no7-line-re-opens|accessdate=2016-07-28|work=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|date=2012-04-02|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022211010/http://www.mta.info/news/2012/04/02/court-square-no7-line-re-opens|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DNA-IRTCourtSq-May12012">{{cite news|last1=Kern-Jedrychowska|first1=Ewa|title=New Court Square Subway Station Design Invites Peeping Toms, Residents Say|url=https://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20120501/long-island-city/new-court-square-subway-station-design-invites-peeping-toms-residents-say|accessdate=2016-07-28|work=[[DNAinfo.com|DNAinfo.com]]|date=2012-05-01|location=[[Long_Island_City|Long Island City]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821160952/https://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20120501/long-island-city/new-court-square-subway-station-design-invites-peeping-toms-residents-say|archivedate=2016-08-21}}</ref>。

