'''法庭廣場-23街車站'''是一個[[IND皇后林蔭路線|IND皇后林蔭路線]]上的地下車站，設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和兩條軌道。位於介乎21街和23街和44徑，是該線在皇后區最西的車站<ref name="MTA-23Ely-Mar172001"/><ref name="MTAMaps-LICQnsBdg-RsvltIs-2015" />。此站最初稱為「21街/范阿爾斯特大道車站」（{{lang|en|21st Street/Van Alst Avenue}}）<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930-pg3">{{cite news|url=http://fultonhistory.com/Newspaper%2015/Brooklyn%20NY%20Daily%20Star/Brooklyn%20NY%20Daily%20Star%201930/Brooklyn%20NY%20Daily%20Star%201930%20-%202104.pdf|title=Court Square Station Of New Tube Completed; War Over Van Alst Ave.|last=|first=|date=1930-07-19|work=Long Island Daily Star|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|page=3|access-date=|via=|accessdate=2016-07-27}}</ref><ref name="LIDaily-23ElyVanAlst-July181932">{{cite news|title=Long Island City Companies Urge Subway Station: Van Alst Avenue Station Held Necessity to Local Labor Needs|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252015%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201932%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201932%2520-%25202721.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F4b10806d4d697f2a22f5b42497a83836#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=Long Island Daily Star|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=1932-07-18|page=5}}</ref>，於1931－1933年間與原先東至羅斯福大道路段一同興建，但{{link-en|紐約市交通局|New York City Board of Transportation}}認為此站缺乏需求，故並未完工，該局更稱之為「死站」<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930-pg3"/><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen1-1939" /><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939" /><ref name="BklynEagle-23Ely-Jan1939" /><ref name="LIDaily-23ElyVanAlst-July181932"/><ref name="Greenpoint-23Ely-Dec1933"/>。然而附近的居民和工廠都嚴重抗議<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930">{{cite news|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252015%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201930%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201930%2520-%25202102.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2Fbf5dfe364c64162631341118e54b9106#page=1|title=Court Square Station Of New Tube Completed; War Over Van Alst Ave.|last=|first=|date=1930-07-19|work=Long Island Daily Star|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|page=1|via=Fulton History|accessdate=2016-07-27}}</ref><ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930-pg3"/><ref name="LIDaily-23ElyVanAlst-July181932"/><ref name="Greenpoint-23Ely-Dec1933"/><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252015%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201930%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Star%25201930%2520-%25202274.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F12924df81ca7950dd4fb191366684ea4#page=1|title=The Case for the Twenty-first Street Station|last=|first=|date=1930-07-31|work=|newspaper=New York Daily Star|page=1|access-date=2016-08-02|via=Fulton History}}</ref>。到了1933年12月，車站易名「埃利大道車站」（{{lang|en|Ely Avenue}}），以免和[[21街車站_(IND跨城線)|鄰近的跨城線車站]]混淆<ref name="Greenpoint-23Ely-Dec1933">{{cite news|title=Power Resumes Campaign To Open Ely Tube Station|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%252023%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Greenpoint%2520Daily%2520Star%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Greenpoint%2520Daily%2520Star%25201933%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Greenpoint%2520Daily%2520Star%25201933%2520a%2520-%25200468.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F7a1979c65dd8184ce04208f9cb55a78e#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=Greenpoint Weekly Star|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=1933-12-15|page=4}}</ref>。1936年9月<ref name="LIDaily-23ElyFinish-Sep1936">{{cite news|title=Ely Ave. Subway Station To Be Completed|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252014%2FJamaica%2520NY%2520Long%2520Island%2520Daily%2520Press%2FJamaica%2520NY%2520Long%2520Island%2520Daily%2520Press%25201936%2FJamaica%2520NY%2520Long%2520Island%2520Daily%2520Press%25201936%2520-%25205316.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F3fd288f9e6cd93d3afe34e6eba7133b7#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=Long Island Daily Press|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=1936-09-13|page=12}}</ref>因車站附近的商業和工業活動擴張，決定將此站繼續興建，安裝瓷磚、樓梯和其他設施<ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen1-1939">{{cite web|title=Subway Station Opens Aug. 28|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9D03EFD9163EE23ABC4D53DFBE668382629EDE|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2015-10-04|date=1939-08-05}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939" /><ref name="BklynEagle-23Ely-Jan1939">{{cite web|title=Award Contract For Subway Work|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/52609334/?terms=%22Ely%2BAve%22%2Bsubway%2Bqueens|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|newspaper=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|accessdate=2015-10-04|page=29|date=1939-01-06|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815103206/https://www.newspapers.com/image/52609334/?terms=%22Ely%2BAve%22%2Bsubway%2Bqueens|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="LIDaily-23ElyFinish-Sep1936"/>。車站於1938年完工，但啟用又再次受缺乏需求影響而延期，並希望車站服務{{link-en|長島市法院|Long Island City Courthouse}}、聖約翰醫院（現時{{link-en|法庭廣場1號|One Court Square}}），以及新啟用的{{link-en|皇后橋住宅|Queensbridge Houses}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Campaign To Open Ely Avenue City Subway Station Renewed; Mayor's Help To Be Sought By Committee; Stop On 8th Avenue Line Was Made Ready Year Ago|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252014%2FLong%2520Island%2520City%2520NY%2520Star%2520Journal%2FLong%2520Island%2520City%2520NY%2520Star%2520Journal%25201939%2FLong%2520Island%2520City%2520NY%2520Star%2520Journal%25201939%2520-%25204356.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2Ffdba307b1d8591208109bba4774f41ef#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=Long Island Star-Journal|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=1939-07-11|page=3}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=New 8th Ave. Station Promised for L.I. City|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%25205%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Eagle%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Eagle%25201939%2520Grayscale%2FBrooklyn%2520NY%2520Daily%2520Eagle%25201939%2520Grayscale%2520-%25205991.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2Fcf2e4aeb76d15913bd248e48830cf76f#page=1|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=[[Brooklyn_Eagle|Brooklyn Eagle]]|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=1939-07-13}}</ref>。

車站於1939年6月28日終於以「23街-埃利大道車站」（{{lang|en|23rd Street–Ely Avenue}}）的名義啟用，剛好是皇后林蔭路線第一段和跨城線法庭街車站啟用後6年<ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen1-1939" /><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939">{{cite web|title=ELY SUBWAY STOP TO OPEN; Queens Station on City-Owned Line Begins Service Tomorrow|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9B0DE0DF1330E53ABC4E51DFBE668382629EDE|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2015-10-04|date=1939-08-26}}</ref>。（埃利大道為23街的舊名<ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939"/><ref name="MTA-23Ely-Mar172001" /><ref name="Greenpoint-23Ely-Dec1933"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stevemorse.org/census/changes/QueensChanges1_EtoF.htm |title=STREET NAME CHANGES* IN QUEENS, NEW YORK |access-date=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125075950/https://stevemorse.org/census/changes/QueensChanges1_EtoF.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1915年皇后區地形局將許多已命名的街道編配數字<ref name="MTA-23Ely-Mar172001">{{cite news|title=23rd Street-Ely Avenue Station becomes Court Square: In Anticipation of New G to 7 Transfer Connection|url=http://www.mta.info/press-release/nyc-transit/23rd-street-ely-avenue-station-becomes-court-square|accessdate=2016-07-27|work=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|date=2011-03-17|archive-date=2019-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812185028/http://www.mta.info/press-release/nyc-transit/23rd-street-ely-avenue-station-becomes-court-square|dead-url=no}}</ref>。）相似地，范阿爾斯特大道是現時21街<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930" /><ref name="NYTimes-23ElyOpen2-1939" /><ref name="NYTimes-LIC-VanAlst-2014">{{cite web|last1=Roberts|first1=Sam|title=Long in Repose, Last Remnants of a Founding Family Will Leave Long Island City|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/04/nyregion/long-in-repose-last-remnants-of-founding-family-van-alst-will-leave-long-island-city.html?_r=0|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2015-11-07|date=2014-11-03|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815181022/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/04/nyregion/long-in-repose-last-remnants-of-founding-family-van-alst-will-leave-long-island-city.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而44徑曾命名為諾特大道<ref name="LIDaily-23ElyVanAlst-July181932"/>。
