'''法庭廣場車站'''，原稱「長島市-法庭廣場車站」（{{lang|en|Long Island City−Court Square}}）<ref name="MTA-23Ely-Mar172001"/>，是[[IND跨城線|IND跨城線]]的北端總站，同時也是最北端的車站<ref>{{NYCS const|timetable|g}}</ref>。雖然G線列車服務以此為總站，但軌道繼續北行並在[[皇后廣場車站_(IND皇后林蔭路線)|皇后廣場車站]]以南匯入皇后林蔭路主線。此段軌道不營運，但直至2010年4月19日，列車一天有幾段時間途經此連接線繼續前往[[森林小丘-71大道車站_(IND皇后林蔭路線)|森林小丘-71大道車站]]<ref name="MTA-GLineReview-2013">{{cite web|title=Review of the G Line|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_LineReview_7_10_13.pdf|website=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|mta.info]]|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-08-02|date=2013-07-10|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226002828/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_LineReview_7_10_13.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013">{{cite web|title=Review of the G Line: Appendices|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-10-28|date=2013-07-10|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127233038/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此地下車站於1933年8月19日啟用<ref name="NYTimes-INDQBLCrstwnOpen-1933"/>，設有一個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和兩條軌道<ref name="LIDaily-INDCtSq-July1930"/>。

車站以南為法庭廣場交匯點。一條中央軌道在兩條跨城線主線之間形成，容許列車以車站任一軌道為總站並調度前往布魯克林<ref name="MTA-GLineReview-2013"/><ref name="MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013"/>這段交匯點於1998年現代化<ref name="MTA-GLineReview-2013"/>。

此月台預計作為2015－2019年資金計劃的一部分無障礙化，安裝一部新的升降機<ref name="Capital Plan 2015-2019">{{cite web|title=MTA Capital Program 2015-2019: Renew. Enhance. Expand.|url=http://web.mta.info/capital/pdf/CapitalProgram2015-19_WEB%20v4%20FINAL_small.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-10-28|date=2015-10-28|archive-date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106022734/http://web.mta.info/capital/pdf/CapitalProgram2015-19_WEB%20v4%20FINAL_small.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/news/pdf/MTA_2017_Preliminary_Budget_July_Financial_Plan_2017_2020_Volume_2.pdf|title=MTA 2017 Preliminary Budget July Financial Plan 2017 –2020 Volume 2|last=|first=|date=July 2016|website=mta.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|access-date=2016-08-06|archive-date=2016-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804012052/http://web.mta.info/news/pdf/MTA_2017_Preliminary_Budget_July_Financial_Plan_2017_2020_Volume_2.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/mta/news/hearings/160823/Description-of-Projects-Booklet.pdf|title=METROPOLITAN TRANSPORTATION AUTHORITY (MTA) NOTICE OF PUBLIC HEARING AND DESCRIPTION OF PROJECTS Tuesday, August 23, 2016 4:30 P.M. Request for Federal Financial Assistance Under the Federal Transportation Authorization For Federal Fiscal Year 2017 Capital Improvement Projects|last=|first=|date=2016-07-28|website=mta.info|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|access-date=2016-08-07|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817204721/http://web.mta.info/mta/news/hearings/160823/Description-of-Projects-Booklet.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。升降機計劃原先預計於2016年開始，但推遲到2019年<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/capitaldashboard/allframenew_head.html?PROJNUM=t7041314&PLTYPE=9|title=Project Description, Budget and Scope|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|date=2016-09-30|accessdate=2017-01-28|archive-date=2019-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813073058/http://web.mta.info/capitaldashboard/allframenew_head.html?PROJNUM=t7041314&PLTYPE=9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
